    <description>Leaf blades 2–10 cm × 5–35+ mm. Involucres 9–12+ × 12–25+ mm. Ray corolla laminae
        6–16 mm. Disc corollas 3–6(–7) mm. Cypselae (1–)3–5(–8) mm; pappi 0.6–3+ mm. 2n = 24, 48,
        60, 72.</description>
